%OPTION  ===>¦ZCMD                                                             +
+
+The example to the      %._____________________________________________________
+right shows display of  %|    Memlist  Functions  Options  Special  Defaults
+ISPF extended           %|+ ---------------------------------------------------
+statistics:             %|+                ¢ MEMLIST Source Member List 3 +
                         %|  Command ===>
                         %|+Enter an ISPF command, a PDS subcommand or a ...
                         %|  - DSN=HABL.LIB.CNTL,VOL=SER=TSO001  MEM=TEMP:TEM  -
                         %|¢ CMD +NAME     ¢DATA      ...  ¢SIZE XSTAT ID+
 +extended stats    ->>  %|!     +SMP      !        $ ... $   9M  Y  TRIDJK
 +   "      "       ->>  %|!     +TEMP02   !        $ ... $ 182K  Y  TRIDJK
 +   "      "       ->>  %|!     +TEMP03   !        $ ... $84552  Y  TRIDJK
 +regular stats     ->>  %|!     +TESTMAMP !        $ ... $ 4211     TRIDJK
 +   "      "       ->>  %|!     +TESTMP2  !        $ ... $65535     TRIDJK
 +   "      "       ->>  %|!     +TEXMP    !        $ ... $   61     TRIDJK
                         %|!                                  %.
+Note:  Point-and-shoot  %|!                                  %.
+column headers are      %|!                                  %.
+sortable.  Subsequent   %|!                         ¢SIZE%Scaling factors:+
+shots will reverse the  %|!                          !K+- thousand (>  99,999)
+sort order.             %|!                          !M+- million  (> 999,999)
